<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Vision & Mission</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .text-content p {
  text-align: justify;
}


    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .section {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .vision {
      background-color: #003366;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .mission {
      background-color: #f7931e;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .text-content {
      flex: 1 1 400px;
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    .text-content h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .text-content p {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .image-content {
      flex: 1 1 300px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .image-content img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .section {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 10px;
      }

      .text-content h2 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      .text-content p {
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      .image-content {
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="section vision">
    <div class="text-content">
      <h2>VISION</h2>
      <p>
        Our institute’s vision is to be a leading educational institution that imbues students with Indian Mind, Indian Culture, and Indian Soul, while preparing them for global citizenship with a strong foundation in values. We recognize that every student has unique strengths and weaknesses, and our goal is to help them overcome their weaknesses and nurture their strengths. Through peer learning and a collaborative environment, we aim to cultivate well-rounded, empathetic global citizens who are capable of making a positive impact in the world. Our curriculum, both academic and extra-curricular, is designed to promote holistic learning, enabling every child to reach their full potential. We hold ourselves accountable to our students and their families, ensuring that their progress is closely tracked through our transparent academic tracking system. Above all, our students’ concepts are clear, lucid, and understood, creating a strong foundation for their lifelong learning journey.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="image-content">
      <img src="/WhoWeAre/Images/Children.png" alt="Vision Image">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section mission">
    <div class="image-content">
      <img src="/WhoWeAre/Images/Children.png" alt="Mission Image">
    </div>
    <div class="text-content">
      <h2>MISSION</h2>
      <p>
        “At Karuna Shanti, we are committed to providing quality education and empowering vulnerable students from
        Tribal, Dalits, and OBC communities. Through our Higher Secondary center for education, SOLID-KASH +3 Science
        center Bijayananda Center (ABC), we empower students to reach their full potential. Our mission is to create
        lasting change in the lives of these students and families through education, equity, and opportunity.”
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
